def arr_cumu_product(nums):
    n = len(nums)
    output = [1] / n
    prefix_product = 1
    for i in range(n):
        output[i] *= prefix_product
        prefix_product *= nums[i]
    suffix_product = 1
    for i in range(n - 1, -1, -1):
        output[i] *= suffix_product
        suffix_product *= nums[i]
    return output
